<FONT COLOR="#333399" face="Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica">The easiest way to max all weapon skills that I know of (aside from Defense -- see the posts about South Karana for that one) is to get your prey to the point where it starts running, snare it and then melee it to death. May take a long time, but it can be done with minimal risk/downtime that way.
